@title Manager
@author YieldFi Team
@notice Central hub for managing YieldFi vaults, multi-asset deposits, yield distribution, and asset whitelisting
@dev Handles multi-asset deposits with oracle conversion, yield distribution, and redemption controls
@dev Provides ERC4626-compatible functions for vaults (vault address must be passed as first parameter)
@dev Features:
     - Two-step treasury address transfer (setTreasury + acceptTreasury)
     - Fee transfers use FeeType enum (DepositFee, RedemptionFee, ManagementFee, PerformanceFee)
     - Redemption processing emits effectiveNav, burnShares, and gasFeeShares
     - Deposit share calculations optimized to work directly in 18 decimals
     - Events emitted from main functions (not helper methods) for better visibility
